INTRODUCTION\b0\par
'Cab Service Management System' is the application used to manage the entire service of Cab booking company. This system greatly simplifies the cab booking process for the customers. System presents an interactive and up-to-date menu with all available options in an easy to use manner. This system helps users to grab cab by accessing their location which reduces the time required for other means of cab services. Also helps the cab drivers to increase their profit when the nearest customers chooses them.\par
 \b PURPOSE OF DOCUMENT\par
\b0 The purpose of this document is that it will provide a detailed description about the system. \par
\par
\b ABOUT THE ORGANISATION\par
\b0 The main objective of this system is to give provision to the cab booking company owner to flourish their business by put together all the cab drivers in an single system.\b\par
